701283f-a.title: Bronx: Home Street - Bryant Avenue
701283f-a.text:
Home Street, north side, east from Bryant Avenue to WWest Farms
Road. At the N.W. corner of the latter thoroughfare is the Home
Street Presbyterian Church.
April 26, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
